      "SLDC cost refers to the SLDC Charges paid to serve the consumers within the area of the supply and not availing supply under Open Access.",
      "Distribution Cost refers to the distribution cost borne by the licensee to serve the consumers within the area of the supply and not availing supply under Open Access.",
      "Inter-state transmission and scheduling expenses to be submitted in this form.",
